creator: Boyou Game
descriptionHtml:
If you like mahjong, puzzle, pictures match, this game is for your . The game contains massive challenging puzzles and well-designed levels. It is simple at the beginning, there will be more challenges as your skills improve. This game will give you a new experience, you need to use good logic and strategy to pass its level. Train brain, exercise logical thinking, increase memory.

👉Tap any square, let it fly onto the board
👉Three same squares will be removed from the board. Clear all squares as soon as possible.
👉When all the squares are cleared, this level is completed!
👉When there are 7 squares on the board, you lose!

💡Features:
✔️100% free games, props are also available in the game
✔️More than 1000 challenging levels, it's a big challenge. (continuously updated)
✔️Play anytime, anywhere, without WiFi.
✔️One finger can play the game.
✔️Variety of exquisite patterns, fruits, cakes, plants, animals, pets. 👻🥑🦋🍰🐱
✔️Train your brain and fingers to bring you happy and fun time.
✔️Fight off boredom

💥💥💥 Let's play this puzzle game with friends! Make easy and enjoy every day!!!
